        "See Pitchstone.",
        "To cover over or smear with pitch.",
        "Fig.: To darken; to blacken; to obscure.",
        "To throw, generally with a definite aim or purpose; to cast; to hurl; to toss; as, to pitch quoits; to pitch hay; to pitch a ball.",
